{"tid":483451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[民主黨]李華明:直播李飛有意義非洗腦 , 政客誇張無限擴大 !","createTime":"2017-11-29T06:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T06:00:52.000Z","uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c5dad371a64622049df98018faabaf3d7ab873f5","tid":483451,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171128/s00001/1511851112670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171128%2Fs00001%2F1511851112670&d=jQ8xyZDsqHejrt5cQn20JP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=9b97aec1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171128%2Fs00001%2F1511851112670&h=172e90ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171128/s00001/1511851112670</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171128/s00001/0da2cf92c5434a14d6be58fe7632a286.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171128%2Fs00001%2F0da2cf92c5434a14d6be58fe7632a286.jpg&h=8af99723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本法委員會主任李飛早前來港就《基本法》演講，教育局鼓勵學校直播，被批評是「洗腦」。不過民主黨李華明指活動有意義，又說一次演講不能做到「洗腦」效果，認為「香港有些政客動不動就會以誇張及無限擴大的說法，指凡是中央官員或特區政府的說話便有洗腦效應」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李華明上周五於《am730》專欄撰寫題為＜催眠的基本法講座＞文章，提到李飛來港演講及教育局要求學校直播，被指摘為「洗腦」。<br />\n<br />\n他說，翻查維基資料，「洗腦」是「透過系統性方法，有意圖地向別人灌輸思想，來符合操縱者的意願，一連串的手法與過程」，惟安排中學生在禮堂聽李飛演講，「肯定不是洗腦！反而我會稱之為最佳的催眠」。<br />\n<br />\n李華明續指，「一次過的演講絕對不能做到洗腦的效果」，只是香港有些政客動不動以「誇張」及「無限擴大」說法，凡是中央官員或特區政府的說話便說有「洗腦」效應，但他表示，「對中學生最具影響力的，便是通識科的老師，網上的資訊及朋輩間的互相影響」。<br />\n<br />\n李華明指，今次是香港回歸20周年活動，「意義是肯定有的」，惟不應該直播，而是事後剪輯，讓老師和同學邊看邊討論，才能把《基本法》深入校園。"},{"pid":"c57a0109f4c05be2b7c6803900a327fa9c0a7a50","tid":483451,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:44:39.000Z","msg":"賣你嘅牛丸啦 嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfb99f7b3b848fb852225a7493c8d9a8f457dc76","tid":483451,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"你都係退黨去痴埋湯生到啦..."},{"pid":"e9264d06cb927e4dd78f0515b904971407193f42","tid":483451,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4cec3ff76c7f574cd0c2c026bacb740b233e38","tid":483451,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T18:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52170de48e959a9d5f1d6d246ff077b2a681cdc6","tid":483451,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}